Responsibilities:

Build and maintain collaborative relationships with all stakeholders of the Institute for Translational Research (ITR) of HKSTP, including but not limited to academia, researchers, and business clients;
Provide instrumentation and application support to Biomedical Technology Support Centre (BSC);  
Assist users in operation and maintenance of laboratory instruments as well as support projects of BSC users;
Handle technical writing such as standard operating procedures, protocols, technical notes, guidelines and flow charts;
Understand customers’ technical requirements and develop effective solutions;
Provide overall administrative and procurement support; and
Perform any other duties as assigned by supervisors and management.

